      "content": "i don't think i can find new meaning. it feels like the color has just been drained out of everything. sometimes i think about him and i just feel this pull, like i'm meant to be where he is. it's the only thing that doesn't feel heavy anymore. the thought of finally being with him again... it's the only thing that sounds peaceful.",
